      "comment": "WHISPERED (1) has been a little hard to follow, missing the frame last time but was a Grade 4/5 winner three starts ago and has drawn 1 where she has won before. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. CAROL RAIN (2) turned in a plain run last time when eighth at Shepparton over 450m behind Paw Monet (25.83) in a Grade 5 H. Placed at her previous run. Better than last start and can bounce back. LAMIA WHEEZE (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Sandown behind Prison Break (29.65) in a Grade 4. Has the pace to be prominent. Must be included in calculations. QUEST FOR ANGEL (8) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
